resources.description: This article describes the selection and arrangement of electromagnetic sensors, and the way of acquiring and processing path information of electromagnetic smart car system. Speed control system uses anti-windup digital PID control algorithm. Actual test shows that this smart car has good stability and high speed.
resources.name: Design of Smart Car System Based on Electromagnetic Sensors
